code: @Override protected BasicCacheContainer createCacheManager() throws Exception {     Properties props = new Properties().     props.setProperty("infinispan.client.hotrod.server_list", "127.0.0.1:11222").     props.setProperty("infinispan.client.hotrod.force_return_values", "true").     return new RemoteCacheManager(new ConfigurationBuilder().withProperties(props).build(), true). }
